Class Vertex

  • java.lang.Object
    • Vertex

  • public class Vertex
extends java.lang.Object
    This class models a vertex in a graph. For ease of the reader, a label for this vertex is required. Note that the Graph object only accepts one Vertex per label, so uniqueness of labels is important. This vertex's neighborhood is described by the Edges incident to it.
